subject: Agreement on the mutual recognition of professional qualifications for architects
precis: Order authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary for Decision No 1/2024 of the Joint Committee on Mutual Recognition of Professional Qualifications of 10 October 2024 setting out an agreement on the mutual recognition of professional qualifications for architects to become binding for Canada.
